## Views

Views handle presentation only - no business logic.

### Page Layout Structure

**Standard Pattern (Required for all pages):**

```erb
<% content_for :title, "Page Title - Vantura" %>

<main id="page-container" aria-label="Page description">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header_simple', title: "Page Title", subtitle: "Page subtitle" %>

  <%= content_wrapper class: "py-6" do %>
    <!-- Page Sections -->
  <% end %>
</main>
```

**Key Components:**

1. **Root Element:** Always use `<main>` tag (not `<div>`) for semantic HTML and accessibility
   - Add `id="[page-name]-container"` following ID naming conventions
   - Add `aria-label` for screen readers
   - Optional: Add `data-controller` attributes if needed for Stimulus

2. **Page Title:** Use `content_for :title` for consistent browser tab titles
   - Format: `"Page Name - Vantura"`

3. **Page Header:** Always use `render 'shared/page_header_simple'`
   - Provides consistent header styling
   - Includes title, subtitle, and quick actions
   - Use `hide_quick_actions: true` if quick actions aren't needed

4. **Content Wrapper:** Always use `content_wrapper` helper (not manual classes)
   - Provides consistent responsive padding and max-width
   - Use `class: "py-6"` or `class: "py-4"` for vertical spacing
   - Never use manual `max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4` classes

5. **Sections:** Use semantic `<section>` elements with proper IDs
   - Format: `id="[context]-[purpose]-section"`
   - Add `aria-label` for accessibility

**Example - Complete Page:**

```erb
<% content_for :title, "Dashboard - Vantura" %>

<main id="dashboard-page-container" aria-label="Dashboard page">
  <%= render 'shared/page_header_simple', title: "Dashboard", subtitle: "Your cash flow projection tool" %>

  <%= content_wrapper class: "py-6" do %>
    <!-- Key Insights Section -->
    <section id="financial-insights-section" class="mb-6" aria-label="Financial insights">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Financial Insights</h2>
      <!-- Section content -->
    </section>

    <!-- Statistics Section -->
    <section id="statistics-section" class="bento-grid mb-6" aria-label="Financial statistics">
      <!-- Statistics content -->
    </section>
  <% end %>
</main>
```

**Why This Pattern:**

- **Consistency:** All pages follow the same structure, making the codebase predictable
- **Accessibility:** Semantic HTML (`<main>`, `<section>`) improves screen reader support
- **Maintainability:** Using helpers (`content_wrapper`, `page_header_simple`) centralizes styling changes
- **Hotwire Compatibility:** Proper structure ensures Stimulus controllers connect correctly
- **Responsive Design:** `content_wrapper` provides consistent responsive behavior

